'''Angie''' is the mother of [[Paige]].

==History==
Angie was shocked to learn that her daughter, Paige, had gotten hepatitis B from letting a boy bite her.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
Her daughter, Paige, got hepatitis B from a bite from her boyfriend. Angie was shocked and questioned Paige about it. Paige refused to tell her the name of the boy who bit her.
